        <mj-text align="center" mj-class="h3" padding="0">Ronald Tuff</mj-text>
        <mj-text align="center" font-size="13px" color="#999999" padding="0 0 8px 0">Businessman</mj-text>
        <mj-text align="center">Far far away, behind the word mountains.</mj-text>
      </mj-column>
      <mj-column>
        <mj-image src="images/person_2.jpg" alt="William Clarson" width="100px" border-radius="50%" align="center" padding="0 0 14px 0" />
        <mj-text align="center" mj-class="h3" padding="0">William Clarson</mj-text>
        <mj-text align="center" font-size="13px" color="#999999" padding="0 0 8px 0">Businessman</mj-text>
        <mj-text align="center">Far far away, behind the word mountains.</mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section background-color="#fafafa" padding="10px 30px 40px 30px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-image src="images/person_3.jpg" alt="Ryan Bean" width="100px" border-radius="50%" align="center" padding="0 0 14px 0" />
        <mj-text align="center" mj-class="h3" padding="0">Ryan Bean</mj-text>
        <mj-text align="center" font-size="13px" color="#999999" padding="0 0 8px 0">Businessman</mj-text>
        <mj-text align="center">A small river named Duden flows by their place and supplies it with the necessary regelialia. It is a paradisematic country, in which roasted parts of sentences fly into your mouth.</mj-text>
